activities.content: left information with Angelina, no information given.

04/30/25 (Rafael) spoke with Claudia, she mentioned the best way to reach out to them, would be through the email on file. Sent them email flyer. He replied shortly, and notified us that he was not interested in our services.
09/19/2025 Rafael emailed them a flyer.
left information with Jasmine, she mentioned they don't need services.
04/30/25 (Rafael) called, no answer and couldn't leave a message.
09/19/2025 Rafael called, number appears to be out of service.
Business was closed took picture.
5/9/25- (Rafael) I could not find the number for this Business, none of the names listed under this address have this name.
05/15/2025 Rafael called, no answer, couldn't leave a message.
left information with Diana, she mentioned to follow up with Cynthia
5/15/25 (Doris) called phone number on file is not in service.
10/09/25- Found second number Online. Updated Log- Jacky
10/27/25 Doris called no answer left voice message.
Left information with employee she mention owner was bussy to come at a earlier time to talk to her. took picture
06/23/2025 Rafael called, spoke with Victoria, she mentioned the owners are out for a week, to call back then to see if they are interested, she mentioned to ask for her or Jose when I call back.

07/11/2025 Rafael called to follow up with owners. Victoria mentioned the owner just left to home depot, that I should call back in 30 minutes. She also mentioned they could use more staff, will try to persuade the owner to get our Service, as per my request.

07/11/2025 Rafael called back, spoke with Victoria, she mentioned the manager said they are fully staffed. She was kind enough to let me know they are adding a bar in the back, To call back in a month, they will need people to man the station.
left information with Rosa, no information given.
05/09/25 Rafael called, spoke with Sarahi, who mentioned they don't need our services at the moment.
left information with Leia, shes interested in payroll service.
01/14/25 (Doris) went to dropped of quote left it with Leia.
03/27/25 Jackie and (Doris) stopped by we spoke with Leia she mention will stay with her payroll but would like to see if we can help her with staffing service.
